name: AUDIO_REVERB_PRESET
description:
Voice reverb presets.Deprecated:
                        Deprecated as of v3.2.0.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_OFF: Turn off voice reverb, that is, to use the original voice.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_KTV: The reverb style typical of a KTV venue (enhanced).

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_VOCAL_CONCERT: The reverb style typical of a concert hall (enhanced).

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_SISTER: The reverb style typical of a young woman's voice.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_STUDIO: The reverb style typical of a recording studio (enhanced).

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_POPULAR: The reverb style typical of popular music (enhanced).

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_RNB: The reverb style typical of R&B music (enhanced).

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_FX_PHONOGRAPH: The voice effect typical of a vintage phonograph.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_POPULAR: The voice effect typical of popular music.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_RNB: The voice effect typical of R&B music.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_ROCK: The reverb style typical of rock music.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_HIPHOP: The reverb style typical of hip-hop music.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_VOCAL_CONCERT: The voice effect typical of a concert hall.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_KTV: The voice effect typical of a KTV venue.

parameters.AUDIO_REVERB_STUDIO: The voice effect typical of a recording studio.

parameters.AUDIO_VIRTUAL_STEREO: The reverberation of the virtual stereo. The virtual stereo is an effect that renders the monophonic audio as the stereo audio, so that all users in the channel can hear the stereo voice effect.
